&lt;li&gt;Support Account Directors with campaign &amp;amp; account management duties&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Analyze direct response performance &amp;amp; compile custom reporting according to customer needs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create, edit, optimize and scale social media campaigns based off complex performance trends&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Train self-serve users on how to best use the Kargo Commerce software&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist with back-end processes such as feed mapping, creative scoping and more&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Troubleshoot technical assets such as product catalogs, pixels, offline data sets and more&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide regular feedback to product team sourced from customers &amp;amp; your own experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Communicate effectively&amp;nbsp; with stakeholders of your accounts on performance, measurement, testing plans, creative opportunities and more&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
